      "message": "This storeName is a variable and as of now, it is not used. Currently the orchestrator code defaults to storename \"orchestrator\": https://gerrit.onap.org/r/gitweb?p=multicloud/k8s.git;a=blob;f=src/orchestrator/pkg/infra/db/store.go;h=1a9632e7ebf027a265b0be18342f0b9f0d3575aa;hb=8af74ae61508a3fbfd54c25d1cfe037f3ad08ca5#l67\n\nFurther this follows the convention set in project api: https://gerrit.onap.org/r/gitweb?p=multicloud/k8s.git;a=blob;f=src/orchestrator/pkg/module/project.go;h=e44164f96208cca7fee12a45e192fa7ce09b60a1;hb=8af74ae61508a3fbfd54c25d1cfe037f3ad08ca5#l60\n\nI assume storeName here was set in case we neeeded to change it sometime in the future. However it is not currently used in the code as far I can tell.",
